The paper presents a tool for verifying systems employing Model Predictive Control (MPC), which is a widely used synthesis technique for constrained and optimal control in industry. The tool provides an automated approach for analyzing these systems for rigorous guarantees of safety. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of systems and control (cs.SY), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), robotics (cs.RO), machine learning (cs.LG), and software engineering (cs.SE).
